drawnet.lib.filters
Class FilterData

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.filters.FilterData
Direct Known Subclasses:
FilterDataGSPN, FilterDataGSPNSta, FilterDataOsMoSysIn, FilterDataOsMoSysIn_Old
public abstract class FilterData
extends java.lang.Object

This is a abstract class to derive from if you need a class to store filter's data. This is meant only for formal reasons and to leave space to add standard methods and utilities in the future. In fact, every filter is different and may require different methods and properties.
